  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037794962-LVNHQWGVWIDS7AW9QA9H/16a-DSC_3309.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>The last time I was in San Diego teaching, I was pregnant. Very pregnant, if there is such a thing. You can see evidence of that in this post. Other than that, the classes were much the same - great people, good times, in a completely creative setting. If you are a fan of paper and are in San Diego, I highly recommend a visit to <a href=\"http://www.papertales.typepad.com/\">Paper Tales</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"16b-1-600x451.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037815015-EVVH2JZFKYRWYR4G3WD6/16b-1-600x451.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"16c-DSC_3306-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037814905-XX7ZUC11QFZW6ZPF13FZ/16c-DSC_3306-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, that is baby Jack (mohawk and all) in my arms and a donut in Kelly's. So appropriate and adorable.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"16d-DSC_3308-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037847857-2QTNBCEUO99JMUKC6CBL/16d-DSC_3308-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16e-DSC_3311-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037847916-ZK56AG7YW49QNXOLOOYC/16e-DSC_3311-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16f-DSC_3312-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037848247-O1EN65CZNWVKGI75WNBS/16f-DSC_3312-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16g-DSC_3329-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037848565-BWHFV7F6GSWP6VG68QGO/16g-DSC_3329-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16h-DSC_3319-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037848678-G8AUYXHORAKZ1NXWQ3SS/16h-DSC_3319-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16i-DSC_3331-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037849132-Z4YQQ8HWHQ02QU2J5UPU/16i-DSC_3331-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16j-DSC_3339-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037849474-YLVYIXFPH31P3ASGK73P/16j-DSC_3339-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16k-DSC_3344-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599037849542-2ATTKDUE0NVML3EI4Z38/16k-DSC_3344-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Loved seeing familiar faces and meeting new ones - some who drove from far away! Once again, if you're on Instagram,we added more photos to the existing <a href=\"http://ink361.com/app/#%21/tag/amykpsandiego\">#amyKPsandiego</a>. Thanks again Michelle - we had a blast! PS- there are just 2 spaces left for my April 12th workshop in Santa Ana- check the sidebar to sign up!</p>"
}